{"tid":1010341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄉議局主席劉業強為香港求得第八十六中籤","createTime":"2019-02-06T02:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:02:47.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f6da78aa2150f25bc71c4db377ddeea651673b16","tid":1010341,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"香港電台-港聞 &middot; 98人追蹤<br />\n1 小時前<br />\n今日是大年初二車公誕，鄉議局主席劉業強按習俗早上率領沙田鄉事委員會代表和鄉紳，到車公廟為香港及沙田區求籤祈福。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強為香港求得第86籤中籤。<br />\n<br />\n籤文內容是「石田為業喜非常，畫餅將來未見香；怎曉田耕耘不得，那知餅食不充腸」。解曰：「出入謹慎，家宅不吉；自身平安，求財不遂」。<br />\n<br />\n沙田鄉事委員會首副主席李志麒則為沙田求得第82籤下籤，籤文內容是「心中日復自思量，時運未通怎主張；進退難為無定處，恐防患禍與災殃」。寓意出入謹慎，凡事小心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中籤都咁衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e3786e3de72aececca866f6ebe22ed9eaa6bce","tid":1010341,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"下下簽黎架"},{"pid":"4048f2090a8e4ea2908aa6eb1d863f4d88fc6949","tid":1010341,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:06.000Z","msg":"解曰「出入謹慎，家宅不吉，自身平安，求財不遂」"},{"pid":"1720ecb893d8d9dd0ad2080eb9abdb14353aad09","tid":1010341,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06e3786e3de72aececca866f6ebe22ed9eaa6bce","tid":1010341,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"下下簽黎架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"下下一早抽走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e147c0fccbd8cef6ceee3159b4b2d2ec3064f5c7","tid":1010341,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"劉業強憑咩代表我地？"},{"pid":"3775a3dacdc4967a8731e3c690479519e0dd95f6","tid":1010341,"uid":57848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4048f2090a8e4ea2908aa6eb1d863f4d88fc6949","tid":1010341,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:39:06.0